name: Fundraising Free Flow Brunch x Keep Vietnam Clean
description:
FUNDRAISING FREE FLOW BRUNCH X KEEP VIETNAM CLEAN 

Celebrate your December with DÃ©glacer and our new friend @keepvietnamclean in an extremely meaningful event - Fundraising Free Flow Brunch. With a mission to promote and inspire sustainable lifestyles and environmental health across Vietnam, Keep Vietnam Clean has engaged 5,244 volunteers, organised 106 clean-up events, collected 314 tons of waste, developed 1,700 m2 of greenspace, recruited 496 citizens to champion environmental improvement, set up 6 demo sites of regenerative farming practices. 

In this event, we invite you to enjoy a new glass of mulled wine with lamb, beef, and fresh seafood plate meals. DÃ©glacer and diners will join forces with Keep Vietnam Clean in fundraising activities for the project "Green Space, Healthy Lifestyle," planting shade trees for almost 900 students and 49 teachers at Phuc Tien Primary School, with 50% of the event profit given to Keep Vietnam Clean.
